sources.description: You can find out more about this movie from Wikipedia . Â  The Raging Tide is a 1951 American Film Noir directed by George Sherman and starring Shelley Winters, Richard Conte, Stephen McNally, Charles Bickford and Alex Nicol. The screenplay was by Ernest K. Gann based on his 1950 novel Fiddler's Green.
